message.body: Hey what do you want to do for dinner tonight? I'm good with going into the city to meet up with Sarah
Alright! My sister has my car now since we had to take her car to the shop so I would need a ride wherever we go :)
Sure! I can see what her plans are
Sarah said before she is in class until 4:45. When she responds I will let you know
From Sarah: Leaving class now and I just want to get out of here! So let's eat around needham
Haha ok. Any ideas of where to go? I'm good with any of our regular places.
Same. I don't know about anything new, do you? Lemon Thai, mandarin cuisine, comellas, pizza...where else do we go
Uh yeah i cant think of anything else. I vote either lemon Thai or comellas
There is also acapulcos...no idea how good or expensive it is
That is true. We can check it out and go there or somewhere else
Cool. I texted Sarah. She is on the t and I'm guessing will text back once she gets signal back.
Nvm she says lemon Thai. I will leave at 6:20.
